   <S PAR='17' RSNT='1' SNO='17'>It is not a light word.</S>
   <S PAR='18' RSNT='1' SNO='18'>Christ is making His home in us.</S>
   <S PAR='19' RSNT='1' SNO='19'>Christ lives in us.</S>
   <S PAR='20' RSNT='1' SNO='20'>But some Christians today don t believe this.</S>
