   <S PAR='26' RSNT='1' SNO='26'>These are ethical teachings.</S>
   <S PAR='27' RSNT='1' SNO='27'>These are not the teachings according to the biblical revelation.</S>
   <S PAR='28' RSNT='1' SNO='28'>LIVING WITH CHRIST IN OUR SPIRIT</S>
   <S PAR='29' RSNT='1' SNO='29'>How then should we live?</S>
   <S PAR='30' RSNT='1' SNO='30'>We must live in a way to avoid or to escape the first person Satan in our flesh.</S>
