   <S PAR='33' RSNT='1' SNO='33'>We should live by the second person.</S>
   <S PAR='34' RSNT='1' SNO='34'>We don t behave ourselves; we live Christ.</S>
   <S PAR='35' RSNT='1' SNO='35'>Sisters, do you behave yourself and conduct yourself in a very nice way, or do you live by Christ in your spirit?</S>
   <S PAR='36' RSNT='1' SNO='36'>Let me illustrate.</S>
